DS folder is the project folder made on Netbeans IDE

first, run the server side
second, run the client side and GUI appears with either to login or signup with an account data saved on a database using JDBC and phpmyadmin, localhost server
third, after a signup action data will be saved to database and cached on pc itself, then UI with products to buy with whatever quantity to specify.
       if a login ,then if it is admin account UI with control of adding, deleting or updating products.
       else products UI and buying action also saved into database
finally, ending the session simply by exiting the application.
